scavenger-convergence = [color=#9cff57]SCANNER:[/color] Too many eyes are tracking the same scrap opportunity. That usually ends one way.
scavenger-dispute = [color=#9cff57]SCANNER:[/color] The argument over salvage rights is getting louder and less civilized by the second.
scavenger-scramble = [color=#ff4444]ALERT:[/color] The scavengers are fighting over the haul. Whatever dropped here was worth bleeding for.
scavenger-split = [color=#9cff57]SCANNER:[/color] The crews split the haul and start backing off before the city notices.
scavenger-fade = [color=#9cff57]SCANNER:[/color] The scav scene is collapsing. Survivors are melting back into the district with their prize.
